game_description: Hello Everyone! Welcome to Dino Runners. This is a action packed fun game that is updated most of the time. This game already has: Cosmetics, Multiplayer, The forest, and many more. This game uses gorilla tag movement and use your hands to move. When you load in, you should see other dinos by your side. (Obviously if anyone is online). Anyway, have fun!
